nodes.text: Rochenda Sandall is a British actress who portrays Chesille Sabrond in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. She is best known for playing crime boss Lisa McQueen on the fifth season of the British police procedural series Line of Duty, and starring in the British drama series Love, Lies and Records.
